Conclusions¶

Devices show normal behaviour.

  • The devices showing higher deviation in temperature are not discarded, as well as noise.
  • PM sensor showing lower PM values had the inlet covered
  • ECOs/VOCS are evaluated for dispersion and show similar trends in indoor environment, although different absolute values, probably related to the stabilisation time
